  <!-- EN: anima affinity -->
  <VRE_AnimaAffinity.label>仙树亲和</VRE_AnimaAffinity.label>
  <!-- EN: Carriers of this gene have a special connection to the anima tree, allowing them to act as an amplifier to the special properties of the tree. They can encourage anima trees to sing, giving everyone in large radius a psychic soothe, as well as help with connection and meditation to it. -->
  <VRE_AnimaAffinity.description>这种基因的携带者与仙树有着特殊的联系，这种联系使其能够放大仙树的特殊能力。他们能够让仙树演奏曲乐，给予半径范围内的所有人一种心灵抚慰，并帮助他们与仙树建立联系和冥想。</VRE_AnimaAffinity.description>
  <!-- EN: Guarantees Natural Meditation focus on the pawn. -->
  <VRE_AnimaAffinity.customEffectDescriptions.0>确保自然冥想聚焦于殖民者。</VRE_AnimaAffinity.customEffectDescriptions.0>
  <!-- EN: Pawns with this gene included in the anima tree linking ritual increase its success by 10% each, stacking up to 5 times. -->
  <VRE_AnimaAffinity.customEffectDescriptions.1>每有1个携带仙树亲和基因的殖民者加入到仙树连接仪式，成功率就会提高10%，最多可提升50%。</VRE_AnimaAffinity.customEffectDescriptions.1>
